issue.title: Participate in Hacktoberfest
issue.body: I wanted to ask if redisson wants to participate in the German hacktoberfest. To participate you can set the HACKTOBERFEST topic/label. You can read more here: https://hacktoberfest.com/participation/

issue.title: Support http status 103 and 425
issue.body:
This PR relates to #8120. There are also quite a few http status codes that got renamed. Even a few common ones like 413. These renames were mostly for consistency reasons and dont give much more information so i believe we should stay with the old ones for backward compatibility right?

This pull request fixes #8120
Signed-off-by: david.scandurra <david.scandurra@check24.de>

comment.body: The Static Analysis Ci fail does not seemed to be related to the changes
